m.youtube.com/watch?v=8COp791i9PQ</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:18:12.000Z","msg":"50mm點解叫35mm等效？咁支鏡叫35mm定叫50mm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T20:05:55.000Z","msg":"支鏡叫35mm<br />\n<br />\n菲林年代135(full frame ff)格式最廣泛，所以大家都用ff 格式下去理解唔同焦距嘅透視<br />\n<br />\n但其實有比ff更大嘅中幅or 大底，有比ff 細嘅apsc apsh 4/3 等，同一個支鏡係唔同底片size 下都有唔同嘅透視感(想像一支ultra wide 鏡影嘅相你會覺得好廣闊，但淨係cut 相中間一細part出嚟嘅話，個廣闊感就冇晒) 要知佢等如ff下咩焦距嘅透視，就要將焦距乘一個比例(eg apsc x1.5, 4/3 x2)<br />\n<br />\n因為支鏡可以同時擺落唔同size 嘅底片機上面，但同一支鏡唔會因為唔同機就轉名，所以只會講支鏡係35mm ，但係apsc 下等同50mm 焦距，係m43 下等同70mm焦距<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有等效景深，即是35f1.4 on apsc 同埋50f1.4 on ff 就算透視(等效焦距)一樣, 光圈一樣，佢地嘅淺景深都唔一樣。實際上35f1.4 on apsc 只有50f2 嘅淺景深效果<br />\n<br />\n但冇等效光圈呢樣野，上面2支鏡計算曝光時都係可以用f1.4去計的"},{"pid":"d1a6e52d7f9ad8baedd8ae259da44f687ecda33b","tid":1659908,"uid":33817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T20:23:50.000Z","msg":"最近睇咗一個street photography YouTuber, 講焦距嘅片<br />\n其實好睇你想影咩，構圖，平時影相習慣呀咁<br />\n可以睇睇參考吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uOACIpWBXEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuOACIpWBXEo&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgJAcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=1e9c9b70\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uOACIpWBXEo</a>"},{"pid":"14c3643febfea14f1d82b52e9cc7916ab33cd3b3","tid":1659908,"uid":174678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb83acdf3bfd245132a6e23cb8744a6d0b202c57","tid":1659908,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9798645ce0dca07fefaae5c634b616bd1dc95de1","tid":1659908,"uid":136023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0eff41d5b470cc0b06470b02c5ae3d39754bb42","tid":1659908,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"用富士計焦距嗰啲好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申用sony同canon"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:49:33.000Z","msg":"咪焦距+焦距/2 有幾難計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T19:22:38